cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
title: "Qubee-IPA-Converter: A Python Library for Converting Oromo Qubee to IPA"
abstract: "A Python library for converting Oromo Qubee orthography to International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA) with built-in quality control. Designed for speech processing, TTS, and computational linguistics."
authors:
